data.description: Highest and Best offers due Monday April 8 at 12:30  pm. This sprawling 5BD/4BA ranch features two master suites, which could be perfect for related living plus you have all primary living space on a single floor with no carpet. This home is built for handicapped accessible living including one of the bathrooms. Let's start the tour: the front door welcomes you into the home's first living room (yes, FIRST living room!) with large windows. From the living room, you can turn left down the hall to three of the bedrooms and two of the bathrooms or straight ahead to the kitchen, sunroom, and balance of the space. Into the kitchen, you have extra counter/prep/serving space with a long counter and another bank of 5 cabinets plus dining space. From the kitchen, you can access the home's sunroom with panoramic views of tranquility! The vaulted ceiling and bank of windows make this space feel EVEN BIGGER than it already is! You also have an exit door to the rear of the home. You can use the sliding glass doors to also step into the home's SECOND living room; this is one of two ways to enter this space. This is an open, airy space that provides access to the sun room and the 2nd master suite with the curbless shower. This master bathroom measures 12x11 and the shower is 7x5! Currently, the homeowners are using this master bedroom space as a home theater. Head downstairs and you'll find ANOTHER bedroom and full bathroom plus loads of storage space, nooks and crannies for stuff you rarely use, and room for a rec room/craft room/family room.  There's honestly space for everyone to enjoy plus the exterior of home has a fantastic lot backing up to farm land with 4-seasons of great viewing. There's a rear deck and also side deck, plus a shed and attached 2+ car garage, too. If you've been looking for the place that offers indoor and outdoor space, a quiet community on the edge of town, and updates for a move-in ready option - this house is waiting to welcome you home. There are 3 sumps and one with battery back up and ejector pump. Roof is 2021. Well pressure tank 2017. 2 Furnace/AC units - one in 91 and the other in 03. 8' garage door. This home did have an elevator and could be reconverted, if needed. 200 amp service. There is a home warranty included with a full price or higher offer.
